/googles-acquisition-of-motorola-is-still-a-bust-and-will-be-for-a-while"> <img height="360" width="640" title="Click here to read Google's Acquisition of Motorola Is Still a Bust And Will Be For a While" alt="Click here to read Google's Acquisition of Motorola Is Still a Bust And Will Be For a While" src="http://img.gawkerassets.com/img/18cboaf33pvmajpg/xlarge.jpg"></a></div> </div> During Google's earnings call today, Google executives made it clear that the acquisition of Motorola comes with quite a bit of baggage. More specifically, Google has "inherited a 12-18 month product pipeline" that Google CFO Patrick Pichette says the company is "still working through." Yikes. <a href="http://gizmodo.com/5978162/googles-acquisition-of-motorola-is-still-a-bust-and-will-be-for-a-while" title="Click here to read more about Google's Acquisition of Motorola Is Still a Bust And Will Be For a While">More&nbsp;&raquo;</a> <br><img width="1" height="1" src="http://gizmodo.feedsportal.com/c/34976/f/647164/s/27cb01f0/mf.gif" border="0"><br><br><a href="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151884962680/u/49/f/647164/c/34976/s/27cb01f0/a2.htm"><img src="http://da.feedsportal.com/r/151884962680/u/49/f/647164/c/34976/s/27cb01f0/a2.img" border="0"></a><img width="1" height="1" src="http://pi.feedsportal.com/r/151884962680/u/49/f/647164/c/34976/s/27cb01f0/a2t.img" border="0"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/gizmodo/full/~4/E2KccDrxRvE" height="1" width="1">";s:9:"feed_link";s:19:"http://gizmodo.com/";s:10:"feed_title";s:7:"Gizmodo";}s:32:"28131bd89843b5ca4811a13e3035da5d";a:7:{s:5:"title";s:55:"CBS Seeks to Unwind Retrans Agreement With Dish Network";s:4:"link";s:66:"http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/thr/news/~3/x1rg4wJhZEg/story01.htm";s:6:"author";s:12:"Eriq Gardner";s:4:"date";i:1358898791;s:7:"content";s:2573:"<img src="http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/sites/default/files/2012/06/new_dish_logo.jpg"><br>In legal papers filed on Tuesday, the network says that Dish concealed facts about th